data.description: Charming two story, 5 bed, 3.5 bath home boasting rustic charm. Embrace the warmth of hardwood floors and wooden accents. Enjoy cooking in the spacious kitchen that leads into dining room. On the main floor you will find 4 spacious bedrooms - two with their own bathrooms and the claw foot bathtub is jetted! Large living room is inviting with tinted PELA windows and an office space. Retreating downstairs into the master suite, a second living area, AND bar. Primary has a built in vanity, large walk in closet, and very generous walk in tiled shower with multiple shower heads. home also features a safe room downstairs. Delight and entertain yourself and guests in the large backyard and approx. 55x16 covered patio and above ground pool. This home has so much to offer take a look today!
